&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;THE GOLDEN RULE&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Whether we’re dealing with colleagues or customers, we follow The Golden Rule, treating others the way we want to be treated. It’s a simple rule, but it’s also significant: we don’t prioritize money or growth over people, and we practice empathy at every opportunity.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;CALM FOCUS&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;We work in tech and build solutions for real estate. Both are fast-paced and stressful industries. So it’s important that&amp;nbsp; we focus on the larger objective rather than rushing from one task to the next. If something is out of scope, we say “No.” If something feels rushed, we pump the brakes. This calm focus helps us create solutions our customers love.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;ONE TEAM, ONE DREAM&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
