&lt;li&gt;The initiative to build something new&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;NMLS licensed held in one or more of the following states: Arizona, Colorado, Florida, Georgia, North Carolina, Oregon, South Carolina, Tennessee, Texas, Washington&lt;/li&gt;
